'''沉睡伊人'''（{{lang-en|'''While She Sleeps'''}}，直譯為'''當她入眠'''）是[[英國|英國]][[金屬核|金屬核]]樂團，2006年成立於[[謝菲爾德|謝菲爾德]]。樂團陣容為[[歌唱|主唱]]{{link-en|勞倫斯·泰勒|Lawrence Taylor}}、[[主音吉他手|主奏吉他手]]{{link-en|西恩·隆恩 (音樂家)|Sean Long (musician)|西恩·隆恩}}、[[節奏吉他手|節奏吉他手]]{{link-en|麥特·威爾許|Mat Welsh}}、[[貝斯手|貝斯手]]{{link-en|亞蘭·麥肯錫|Aaran McKenzie}}、[[鼓手|鼓手]]{{link-en|亞當·薩維奇 (音樂家)|Adam Savage (musician)|亞當·薩維奇}}。他們目前是英國的[[獨立樂團|獨立樂團]]，並分別與[[美國|美國]]的{{link-en|銳音唱片|SharpTone Records}}和[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]的{{link-en|標準唱片|UNFD}}簽約。他們的第一張作品是2010年發行的[[迷你專輯|迷你專輯]]《{{link-en|荒蕪北境|The North Stands for Nothing}}》。2012年發行第一張[[錄音室專輯|錄音室專輯]]《{{link-en|撒旦魔咒|This Is the Six}}》、2015年發行第二張錄音室專輯《{{link-en|狂音穿腦|Brainwashed (While She Sleeps album)}}》、2017年發行第三張錄音室專輯《{{link-en|你也是凡人|You Are We}}》。在{{link-en|2012年Kerrang!音樂獎|Kerrang! Awards 2012}}中，樂團榮獲「最佳英國本土新秀獎」。

== 歷史 ==
=== 組建與《荒蕪北境》（2006 - 2011年） ===
2006年在[[英國|英國]][[謝菲爾德|謝菲爾德]]近郊，[[歌唱|主唱]]{{link-en|喬丹·威多森|Jordan Widdowson}}、[[鼓手|鼓手]]{{link-en|亞當·薩維奇 (音樂家)|Adam Savage (musician)|亞當·薩維奇}}、[[貝斯手|貝斯手]]{{link-en|亞蘭·麥肯錫|Aaran McKenzie}}、[[吉他手|吉他手]]{{link-en|西恩·隆恩 (音樂家)|Sean Long (musician)|西恩·隆恩}}及{{link-en|麥特·威爾許|Mat Welsh}}組建了沉睡伊人。在這支樂團成立之前，這五位成員就已經在不同的樂團中一起演奏過，麥特·威爾許表示：「沉睡伊人是我們離開學校後遇到最棒的夥伴，我們是一個非常緊密的團體」<ref name="SB">{{cite news |last = Territt |first = Katie |title = Stereoboard speak to While She Sleeps about new album 'This Is The Six' & breaking their mold! |publisher = Stereoboard |date = 2012-05-17 |url = http://www.stereoboard.com/content/view/172662/9 |accessdate = 2012-06-03 |archive-date = 2013-12-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131203020747/http://www.stereoboard.com/content/view/172662/9 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。經過幾次的現場表演後，大部分成員在2009年決定全神貫注在樂團裡，成為全職樂手<ref>{{cite video |title = Interview: While She Sleeps |url = https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QQ46ZxXYnBs |publisher = Hit The Floor Magazine |accessdate = 2012-04-03 |time = 1:30 |archive-date = 2014-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140523224019/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QQ46ZxXYnBs |dead-url = no }} {{Wayback|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QQ46ZxXYnBs |date=20140523224019 }}</ref>。然而，由於主唱喬丹·威多森決定繼續工作賺錢，選擇離開了樂團<ref>{{cite web |last=McKenzie |first=Aaran |title=WSS Bassist confirms reasons behind previous vocalists departure |date=2012-06-06 |url=https://twitter.com/AaranWSS/status/210409610631319553 |accessdate=2012-06-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68DrvLK6d?url=https://twitter.com/AaranWSS/status/210409610631319553 |archivedate=2012-06-06 }}</ref>。隨著新主唱{{link-en|勞倫斯·泰勒|Lawrence Taylor}}加入，樂團開始在自家創作[[迷你專輯|迷你專輯]]，並持續進行表演，地點遍及英國後，他們也進入[[歐洲|歐洲]]國家演出<ref>{{cite web |title = While She Sleeps |publisher = The Agency Group |year = 2010 |url = http://www.theagencygroup.com/artist.aspx?ArtistID=6189 |accessdate = 2012-06-03 |archive-date = 2012-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120502101505/http://www.theagencygroup.com/artist.aspx?ArtistID=6189 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。隨著樂迷不斷增加，樂團在2010年7月26日透過{{link-en|小鎮唱片|Small Town Records}}發行迷你專輯《{{link-en|荒蕪北境|The North Stands for Nothing}}》。6月24日，沉睡伊人在家鄉舉行一場專輯發行會，隨後在2010年展開巡迴演唱會<ref>{{cite news |title = While She Sleeps – The North Stands for Nothing. Album Launch. |publisher = The Plug |date = 2010-06-24 |url = http://www.the-plug.com/events-and-tickets/live/while-she-sleeps-north-stands-nothing-album-launch |accessdate = 2012-05-03 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101104101907/http://www.the-plug.com/events-and-tickets/live/while-she-sleeps-north-stands-nothing-album-launch |archivedate = 2010-11-04 }}</ref>，期間受邀登上了{{link-en|音球音樂節|Sonisphere Festival}}<ref>{{cite news |last = Bezer |first = Terry |title = Sonisphere Review: Motley Crue, Audrey Horne, While She Sleeps |publisher = {{link-en|Metal Hammer|Metal Hammer}} |date = 2010-08-10 |url = http://www.metalhammer.co.uk/news/sonisphere-motley-crue-incoming-favourites/ |accessdate = 2012-06-03 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130405140943/http://www.metalhammer.co.uk/news/sonisphere-motley-crue-incoming-favourites/ |archivedate = 2013-04-05 }}</ref>。10月份，他們與{{link-en|傲戰唱片|Good Fight Entertainment}}簽署合約，在美國發行唱片<ref>{{cite news |title = While She Sleeps signs with Good Fight Music |publisher = {{link-en|Blabbermouth.net|Blabbermouth.net}} |date = 2010-10-15 |url = http://legacy.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=147760 |accessdate = 2012-06-03 |archive-date = 2013-01-04 |archive-url = https://archive.is/20130104193820/http://legacy.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=147760 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

隨著迷你專輯的發行，以及廣泛的巡迴演唱會下，沉睡伊人受歡迎的程度不斷升高，媒體和唱片公司的興趣也隨之增加。2011年2月15日，樂團在[[麥達維爾錄音棚|麥達維爾錄音棚]]錄製了[[BBC廣播一台|英國廣播公司廣播一台]]的現場表演節目<ref>{{cite web |last = Carter |first = Daniel P. |title = While She Sleeps In Session |publisher = [[英國廣播公司|英國廣播公司]] |date = 2011-02-15 |url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00y6gyw |accessdate = 2012-06-03 |archive-date = 2020-08-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200806105459/https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00y6gyw |dead-url = no }}</ref>。2011年，樂團一邊巡演一邊創作新作品。3月15日，透過傲戰唱片發行[[單曲|單曲]]〈{{link-en|信任與欺騙|Be(lie)ve}}〉<ref>{{cite web |title = Be(lie)ve – single |publisher = [[iTunes|iTunes]] |date = 2011-03-15 |url = http://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/be-lie-ve-single/id422755327 |accessdate = 2012-06-03 |archive-date = 2012-08-18 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120818104554/http://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/be-lie-ve-single/id422755327 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。5月4日，沉睡伊人受邀擔任[[飛越地平線樂團|飛越地平線]]的暖場團<ref>{{cite news |last = Reid |first = Sean |title = Parkway Drive and While She Sleeps Added to BMTH Sheffield Show |publisher = Alter The Press! |date = January 2011 |url = http://www.alterthepress.com/2011/01/parkway-drive-and-while-she-sleeps.html |accessdate = 2012-06-03 |archive-date = 2014-07-14 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714170258/http://www.alterthepress.com/2011/01/parkway-drive-and-while-she-sleeps.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。同年夏季，樂團受邀到歐洲的幾個音樂節中表演，並在8月底在愛爾蘭擔任飛越地平線兩場表演的暖場團。同時，飛越地平線邀請沉睡伊人參加8月至10月份的美國巡演行程。不過後來因為通關問題不得不取消美國的演出<ref>{{cite news |title = While She Sleeps Forced To Cancel US Tour |publisher = Legends Arising |date = 2011-08-20 |url = http://legendsarising.com/2011/08/20/while-she-sleeps-forced-to-cancel-us-tour/ |accessdate = 2012-06-03 |archive-date = 2014-07-14 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714181732/http://legendsarising.com/2011/08/20/while-she-sleeps-forced-to-cancel-us-tour/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。10月，樂團在英國和歐洲舉行了自己第一次大型巡迴演唱會<ref>{{cite video |title = While She Sleeps Headline Tour October 2011! |publisher = While She Sleeps |date = 2011-09-30 |url = https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NSCxFlzxFCk |access-date = 2017-05-31 |archive-date = 2016-07-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160730154352/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NSCxFlzxFCk |dead-url = no }} {{Wayback|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NSCxFlzxFCk |date=20160730154352 }}</ref>。

=== 《撒旦魔咒》（2012 - 2014年） ===
[[File:Lawrence_Taylor_of_While_She_Sleeps.jpg|thumb]]
2011年11月1日，樂團開始錄製第一張專輯，與製作人{{link-en|卡爾·布恩|Carl Bown}}合作<ref>{{cite news |title = While She Sleeps studio diary Part 1 |publisher = {{link-en|Rock Sound|Rock Sound}} |date = 2011-11-11 |url = http://www.rocksound.tv/news/article/while-she-sleeps-studio-diary-part-1 |accessdate = 2012-06-03 |archive-date = 2011-11-14 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111114022330/http://www.rocksound.tv/news/article/while-she-sleeps-studio-diary-part-1 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。他們首先在英國[[林肯郡|林肯郡]]錄音，之後轉移到[[切斯特菲爾德|切斯特菲爾德]]錄製其餘的部分<ref>{{cite news |title = While She Sleeps studio diary Part 2 |publisher = Rock Sound |date = 2011-12-06 |url = http://www.rocksound.tv/news/article/while-she-sleeps-studio-diary-part-2 |accessdate = 2012-06-03 |archive-date = 2012-01-10 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120110205342/http://www.rocksound.tv/news/article/while-she-sleeps-studio-diary-part-2 |dead-url = no }}</ref>、鋼琴的部分則前往[[威爾斯|威爾斯]]錄製<ref>{{cite news |title=Today we are in Wales recording the final piano parts |publisher=While She Sleeps |date=2012-02-01 |url=http://www.wssofficial.com/post/16864241268/today-we-are-in-wales-recording-the-final-piano |accessdate=2012-06-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68OrJVQCc?url=http://www.wssofficial.com/post/16864241268/today-we-are-in-wales-recording-the-final-piano |archivedate=2012-06-13 }}</ref>。錄音結束後，樂團於2012年2月展開英國巡演，包括{{link-en|Kerrang!巡迴演唱會|Kerrang!#Kerrang.21 Tour}}，與{{link-en|光宗耀祖|New Found Glory}}、{{link-en|暈眩樂團|The Blackout (band)}}等樂團同場<ref>{{cite news |title = Check out the new While She Sleeps track! |publisher = {{link-en|Kerrang!|Kerrang!}} |date = 2012-04-02 |url = http://www.kerrang.com/blog/2012/04/wss_track.html |accessdate = 2012-06-05 |archive-date = 2012-06-14 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120614005635/http://www.kerrang.com/blog/2012/04/wss_track.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。3月27日，樂團宣布與突襲唱片簽約，由該公司發行即將推出的首張專輯<ref>{{cite news |title = Brand New Sony Music/Raw Power Management Label ‘Search & Destroy’ Sign Don Broco & While She Sleeps |publisher = Hit The Floor Magazine |date = 2012-03-27 |url = http://www.hitthefloor.co.uk/rock-metal/brand-new-sony-musicraw-power-managament-label-search-destroy-sign-don-broco-while-she-sleeps/ |accessdate = 2012-06-05 }}{{Dead link|date=2020年6月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。4月4日，英國音樂雜誌《{{link-en|Kerrang!|Kerrang!}}》透露了首張專輯的名稱和發行日期<ref>{{cite news |title= While She Sleeps reveal details of their new album |work=Kerrang! |date= 2012-04-04}}</ref>，但後來實際發行日期又延後了數日<ref>{{cite web|title=Important News For This Is The Six|url=http://www.wssofficial.com/post/28329010655/important-news-for-this-is-the-six|publisher=wssofficial|accessdate=2012-08-07|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130209195556/http://www.wssofficial.com/post/28329010655/important-news-for-this-is-the-six|archivedate=2013-02-09}}</ref>。

5月13日，專輯主打歌〈撒旦魔咒〉發行為單曲<ref>{{cite news |title = While She Sleeps To Release New Single ‘This Is The Six’ |publisher = Metal Hammer |date = 2012-05-01 |url = http://www.metalhammer.co.uk/news/while-she-sleeps-to-release-new-single-this-is-the-six/ |accessdate = 2012-06-13 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120606184846/http://www.metalhammer.co.uk/news/while-she-sleeps-to-release-new-single-this-is-the-six/ |archivedate = 2012-06-06 }}</ref>。與此同時，樂團展開了英國和歐洲各地的巡迴演出，包括他們第一次受邀參加了{{link-en|下載音樂節|Download Festival}}<ref>{{cite news |last = Stickler |first = Jon |title = Download Festival Reveals Stage Times |publisher = Stereoboard |date = 2012-06-01 |url = http://www.stereoboard.com/content/view/172966/9 |accessdate = 2012-06-05 |archive-date = 2014-11-01 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141101050906/http://www.stereoboard.com/content/view/172966/9 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。7月底至8月初，樂團第一次到[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]進行巡迴演出<ref>{{cite news |title = House vs. Hurricane + While She Sleeps + Northlane + Heights |publisher = Loud |date = 2012-05-17 |url = http://www.loudmag.com.au/content/house-vs-hurricane-while-she-sleeps-northlane-heights |accessdate = 2012-06-05 }}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。2012年6月7日，樂團榮獲{{link-en|2012年Kerrang!音樂獎|Kerrang! Awards 2012}}「最佳英國本土新秀獎」<ref name="Kawards12"/>。2012年8月13日，發行第一張[[錄音室專輯|錄音室專輯]]《{{link-en|撒旦魔咒|This Is the Six}}》，登上[[英國專輯排行榜|英國專輯排行榜]]第27名<ref name="UK Album Chart">{{cite news |title = WHILE SHE SLEEPS full Official Chart History |publisher = [[英國專輯排行榜|英國專輯排行榜]] |url = http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/7563/while-she-sleeps/ |accessdate = 2017-05-31 |archive-date = 2017-05-21 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170521192012/http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/7563/while-she-sleeps/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。9月，樂團持續英國巡演行程，10月在歐洲演出。2013年初，第一次受邀登上了澳大利亞{{link-en|聲浪音樂節|Soundwave (Australian music festival)}}。接著，樂團在美國、[[加拿大|加拿大]]和英國擔任{{link-en|飆風大道樂團|Parkway Drive}}的暖場團，以及登上[[Warped巡迴|乖戾巡迴]]音樂節。
